    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/d6f87aa631e645f160f74d6509f665d5.avif?t=1772193603\" width=1280 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/ac3fc13d8c88c0568306eee12b90be7e.poster.avif?t=1772193603\" width=1170 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/ac3fc13d8c88c0568306eee12b90be7e.webm?t=1772193603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/ac3fc13d8c88c0568306eee12b90be7e.mp4?t=1772193603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>ARMS OF GOD: 装备整齐，在这款动作类 roguelite 自动射击游戏中开启一场史诗级的地狱之战。最多可同时使用五种武器，通过升级与融合，打造所向披靡的组合，追求极致火力。肩负神圣使命，化身神的正义，拯救濒临混乱的世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/29b3b28cf60ab29966ea1ff7135a9a13.avif?t=1772193603\" width=1280 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/b87dcf0958813f172da6a6c9559a1cb3.poster.avif?t=1772193603\" width=1170 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/b87dcf0958813f172da6a6c9559a1cb3.webm?t=1772193603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/b87dcf0958813f172da6a6c9559a1cb3.mp4?t=1772193603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时发起远程和近战攻击，操控多达 5 种神圣‘武器’。在面对恶魔群袭时不断变强——圣化你的武器，利用机械臂执行神的意志，从地狱烈火中拯救凡间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/e2249e62636388edd50ee8dfa661a06a.avif?t=1772193603\" width=1280 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/8463c3e922e3548e225d43dd58d6190c.poster.avif?t=1772193603\" width=1170 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/8463c3e922e3548e225d43dd58d6190c.webm?t=1772193603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/8463c3e922e3548e225d43dd58d6190c.mp4?t=1772193603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带来深度满足感的血腥系统在《神之武装》中，每一种敌人都构成独特的挑战。每个生物拥有独特的技能、攻击模式和行为，使每场战斗都成为策略与技巧的试炼。调整战术，从每次对决中吸取经验，展现你对地狱军团的掌控力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/a0f7c7910cdd56122d61cbed751960bb.avif?t=1772193603\" width=1280 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/4c6426ddc9a44929963c2389aa35aae7.poster.avif?t=1772193603\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/4c6426ddc9a44929963c2389aa35aae7.webm?t=1772193603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/4c6426ddc9a44929963c2389aa35aae7.mp4?t=1772193603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从60种独特武器中选择 - 远程与近战一应俱全 - 学习残酷的强化与融合方式，将多件武器合成为一把怪物般的兵器，打造足以抹杀恶魔群与高大头目的恐怖BD。将武器与升级自由搭配，锻造出更多出人意料的组合并发掘隐藏的协同效果。<strong></strong><br><br><br><br><strong>   </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/073389ed761c732a497f5673032a8e80.avif?t=1772193603\" width=1209 height=170 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/19b8234bae28057114f9c3983f3707a5.poster.avif?t=1772193603\" width=1170 height=602 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/19b8234bae28057114f9c3983f3707a5.webm?t=1772193603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/19b8234bae28057114f9c3983f3707a5.mp4?t=1772193603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>   </strong><br>收复并强化圣教总部开启你的圣战，从恶魔之爪中收复圣教总部——大教堂。一旦解放，这座神圣的堡垒将成为你元进程的战略基地。你将在训练场磨练技能，提升元属性；在武器库锻造强大武器；在炼金室增强能力；从钟楼召唤新的勇敢英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/386d89afd37a191d4f1cb1dd040999d5.avif?t=1772193603\" width=1280 height=170 /></span><strong>  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/b85fed1fcc7d6a96ad0402c73a4b835d.poster.avif?t=1772193603\" width=1170 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/b85fed1fcc7d6a96ad0402c73a4b835d.webm?t=1772193603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100310/extras/b85fed1fcc7d6a96ad0402c73a4b835d.mp4?t=1772193603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>元进程系统、剧情发展与成就从 10 位独特英雄中选择，每位英雄都拥有能够改变游戏体验的独特能力。通过元进程系统提升等级，进化角色，踏上通往地狱深渊的道路，在那里面对终极邪恶力量。穿越60个精心打造的关卡，遍布各具特色的场景。废墟、遗物与末日的伤痕本身就在讲述故事片段，逐步揭示人类灭亡背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>我实在告诉你们，我们是上帝的臂膀，执行祂在地上的旨意。因为主上帝大有力量，祂的臂膀为祂施行公义。 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级并融合武器，打造坚不可摧的组合，探索创意搭配，追求极致力量。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在60个独特的场景中，与各种敌人和史诗级头目展开激烈战斗。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>操控10位各具特色的角色，每位角色的能力带来截然不同的游戏体验。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精雕细琢的3D角色；以暗黑和地狱风格呈现的视觉享受。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Steam Deck 上运行表现出色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非常适合单手游玩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单人游戏体验，沉浸式体验。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>引人入胜又轻松的自动射击体验。</strong></p></li></ul>",
